You can ask Penn Bus Tracker the following services:
- Penn Bus East
- Penn Bus West
- Penn Shuttle East
- Penn Shuttle West A
- Penn Shuttle West B

Detailed operational schedule can be found at http://cms.business-services.upenn.edu/transportation
